{"tid":2033631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍老母想洗我腦 求指救","createTime":"2020-05-24T18:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T11:42:58.000Z","uid":357868,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2edbac81ef14870cc5c9bc18bac572ceaf72d5bb","tid":2033631,"uid":357868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"老豆老母深藍 試過因為政見唔同郁手郁腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆話如果佢係警務處處長 一定好早已經開槍 <br />\n又話721佢睇cctvb冇見到白衫打人 831黑警冇可能打死人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從此同佢關係破裂（勁憎佢 打到我瘀撚哂）<br />\n然後老母時不時想借啲依洗我腦 有外國勢力參與一切 話中大條橋 有啲鬼佬指揮喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蔡英文係賤女人 係佢影響啲學生搞革命佢先上到位<br />\n<br />\n今日講國安法啦 佢話 美國夠有國安法 點解佢立得 香港唔立得 佢憑咩干預香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國家安全法 保障我地 有咩唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咗特區護照 有咩唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你會無啦啦顛覆國家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你會分裂國家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同場加映 我哋又唔係逃犯 點解要反逃犯條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國不知幾好 香港係屬於中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇佢地我地冇水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話中國咁玻璃心 香港前面冇加中國兩隻字都拉得<br />\n一個文明社會係唔會得一種聲音 有人抗爭你就滅聲 咁叫咩言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之阻佢搵食就唔得 全部都係暴徒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我點樣可以收佢皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問過佢做乜唔死番大陸 佢一句話點解係佢走 你地班人唔滿意香港就自己走 <br />\n求指教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059d7bd6d1398e6e0c8bbd1086618f38f0ba2467","tid":2033631,"uid":357868,"like":0,"dislike":0,