比人洗腦 係有暴徒搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060f72220f0b93d781ddcd570734dfd4a20d95cb","tid":2033631,"uid":357868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4354d85557bec47961797fa4aa7b09df369797ee","tid":2033631,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:01:42.000Z","msg":"轉貼隔離post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/795221/form-rn-04-2019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F795221%2Fform-rn-04-2019.pdf&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=0a2abacc\" target=\"_blank\">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/795221/form-rn-04-2019.pdf</a><br />\n下次再見嘈印定叠呢啲form 佢地一再講外國勢力之類就叫佢地即場簽撚咗張form直接renounce個BNO或者BC"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:14:49.000Z","msg":"高招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔知佢會有咩反應 會唔會話一早已經冇咗<br />\n又會話我邊度學番嚟對抗父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過！我而加就印定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512b678a40d96f0d6f166dba4a6b781c7bf89c4b","tid":2033631,"uid":357868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93ef11759c9f37867e0027cccbecd8044a7157a0","tid":2033631,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2edbac81ef14870cc5c9bc18bac572ceaf72d5bb","tid":2033631,"uid":357868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"老豆老母深藍 試過因為政見唔同郁手郁腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 