全所以先要立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw多謝你咁有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72675d276edcb205a1e664f05f9880e35d42e6da","tid":2033631,"uid":203491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05611b476a19d78c866035efda697bffd8207ba5","tid":2033631,"uid":357868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f636b8605e0c1a2ad1fb6f7555a39876b94dd14","tid":2033631,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T19:10:01.000Z","msg":"老豆老母有冇錢？<br />\n定係公屋廢老？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T19:43:04.000Z","msg":"老豆公務員 屋企中產 <br />\n成日話自己捱苦捱到今日 學生未出嚟見人世就搞暴亂 多得尼班人唔少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日話自由同民主比唔比到飯你食呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:33:38.000Z","msg":"唔再係國際金融城市，同深圳珠海廣州冇咩分別憑咩搵5位數人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問佢準備好搵5-6000蚊個月未"},{"pid":"65525f7f7a468c6c45e64ec48b179baaf6e2b644","tid":2033631,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2edbac81ef14870cc5c9bc18bac572ceaf72d5bb","tid":2033631,"uid":357868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"老豆老母深藍 試過因為政見唔同郁手郁腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆話如果佢係警務處處長 一定好早已經開槍 <br />\n又話721佢睇cctvb冇見到白衫打人 831黑警冇可能打死人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從此同佢關係破裂（勁憎佢 打到我瘀撚哂）<br />\n然後老母時不時想借啲依洗我腦 有外國勢力參與一切 話中大條橋 有啲鬼佬指揮喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蔡英文係賤女人 係佢影響啲學生搞革命佢先上到位<br />\n<br />\n今日講國安法啦 佢話 美國夠有國安法 點解佢立得 香港唔立得 佢憑咩干預香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國家安全法 保障我地 有咩唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咗特區護照 有咩唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你會無啦啦顛覆國家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.